# Task Manager App

A simple task manager web app that lets users add, complete, filter, and clear tasks.

## Features
- Add new tasks
- Mark tasks as completed
- Filter tasks (e.g., All / Active / Completed)
- Clear completed tasks
- Data persistence using Local Storage

## Demo
- Live URL: (https://task-manager-t6id.onrender.com)
- Repository: (https://github.com/GbosiSophia/task-manager)

## Tech Stack
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript 

## How to Run Locally
1. Download or clone the repo
2. Open the project folder
3. Run it:
   - Easy method: double-click `index.html`
   - Better method: use Live Server in VS Code.

## Usage
1. Type a task in the input box
2. Click 'Add' 
3. Click a task to mark as done
4. Use the filter dropdown to view tasks
5. Use 'Clear Completed' to remove finished tasks

